snippet.title: The Joy of Creation: Halloween Edition | Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
The Joy of Creation: Halloween Edition | Gameplay Teaser

SpringTrap is back! 

The metal groans and shrieks, the flesh rips and breaks, the body on it's very last stand, but the desire of vengeance...stronger then ever before!
Now it's HIS turn.

Support the game: http://gamejolt.com/games/the-joy-of-creation-halloween-edition/202196

Releasing 31st of October, 8 PM CEST.
